<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
	<LanguageData>
		<!-- EN: liquor brewing -->
		<VBE_LiquorBrewing.label>烈酒酿造</VBE_LiquorBrewing.label>
		<!-- EN: Utilize advanced brewing techniques that allow distillation and fermenting of harder spirits with unique effects. -->
		<VBE_LiquorBrewing.description>允许用蒸馏法酿造度数更高的烈酒。</VBE_LiquorBrewing.description>
		<!-- EN:
			<li>subject->the symphony of flavors</li>
			<li>subject_story->mastered the electric alchemy of mixology, blending science and art to stir the soul with every sip</li>
			<li>subject_story->introduced an era of sophistication in drink, where the bar becomes a stage for the dance of flavors</li>
			<li>subject_story->engineered machines for perfect fermenting and bottling, ensuring each concoction is a masterpiece</li>
			<li>subject_story->pioneered the creation of cocktails that are not merely drinks, but experiences, evoking moments and memories</li>
			<li>subject_gerund->crafting elixirs that captivate the senses, blending tradition with innovation at the bar workbench</li>
		-->
		<VBE_LiquorBrewing.generalRules.rulesStrings>
			
			<li>subject->炼酒术</li>
			<li>subject_story->复苏了古代的蒸馏之法，将酒精炼成能一口暖和全身的神奇饮料</li>
			<li>subject_story->让酿酒从简单的发酵变成了一门复杂的手艺，创造出口味无比深邃的酒饮</li>
			<li>subject_story->开发出了工匠精神的最后遗产，每一滴酒都诉说了它的故事</li>
			<li>subject_gerund->将酒的精华呈现在你的面前</li>
		</VBE_LiquorBrewing.generalRules.rulesStrings>
		
		<!-- EN: mixology -->
		<VBE_MixologyResearch.label>调酒</VBE_MixologyResearch.label>
		<!-- EN: Allows construction of advanced machines that utilize electricity for perfect fermenting, industrial bottling, and the mixing of cocktails at the bar workbench. -->
		<VBE_MixologyResearch.description>更先进的知识酿酒，可以使用工业机器蒸馏和装瓶饮料。允许调酒台来调配鸡尾酒。</VBE_MixologyResearch.description>
		<!-- EN:
			<li>subject->the alchemy of spirits</li>
			<li>subject_story->harnessed the ancient secrets of distillation, refining the craft to produce spirits that warm the soul and embolden the heart</li>
			<li>subject_story->elevated brewing from simple fermentation to an art form, creating liquors with unparalleled depth and character</li>
			<li>subject_story->cultivated a legacy of craftsmanship, where each drop tells the story of its making</li>
			<li>subject_gerund->distilling the essence of tradition into spirits of distinction</li>
		-->
		<VBE_MixologyResearch.generalRules.rulesStrings>
			<li>subject->酒香的共鸣</li>
			<li>subject_story->研发出了调酒的技术，将科学与艺术的结晶浓缩成杯中的一小口</li>
			<li>subject_story->让饮料不再单调，让吧台变成舞台</li>
			<li>subject_story->造出了一台机器，专门用来调酒装瓶，让每一杯都成为独一无二的杰作</li>
			<li>subject_story->成为了鸡尾酒的先驱，做出的不仅是酒，更是生活的酸甜苦辣</li>
			<li>subject_gerund->制作充盈五感的奇迹之水，在小小的吧台后面制造一场奇迹</li>
		</VBE_MixologyResearch.generalRules.rulesStrings>
		<!-- EN: espresso machine -->
		<VBE_EspressoMachine.label>咖啡机</VBE_EspressoMachine.label>
		<!-- EN: A more sophisticated method of brewing coffees and teas by using pressurized water. -->
		<VBE_EspressoMachine.description>用高压沸水快速冲泡咖啡和茶的机器。</VBE_EspressoMachine.description>
		
	</LanguageData>
